Shadow Star mumbled to himself to low for anyone to
hear.

Shadow Star:  Why would the Inferno allow this.  The
real opportunities were on the homefront.  The only
reason I accepted this job was so I wouldn't be dubbed
a coward and doomed to gruntwork for the rest of my
immortal life.
